PrecisOrder amending the REGULATORY CAPITAL (BANKS) REGULATIONS and the TOTAL ASSETS (BANKS) REGULATIONS so as to make it clear that the accounting methods referred to therein are the generally accepted accounting principles (GAPP), as modified by the Superintendent, and that prescribed subsidiaries are exempted from various calculations.
